            <li>Streetwear Collections</li>
            <li>Hoodies & Sweatshirts</li>
            <li>Graphic Tees</li>
            <li>Limited Edition Drops</li>
            <li>Fashion Accessories</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Premium Quality Fabrics</li>
            <li>Unique Streetwear Designs</li>
            <li>Comfortable & Durable Apparel</li>
            <li>Trend-Driven Collections</li>
            <li>Customer-First Experience</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            To empower individuals through fashion and help them express
            themselves fearlessly while maintaining exceptional quality,
            affordability, and style.
        </p>
